<jats:list-item><jats:p><jats:italic>Synthesis</jats:italic>. Evaluating the costs and benefits of synzoochory for plant populations under different ecological contexts will help to understand the ecological principles of the interaction but also allows to move the interaction towards each end of the antagonism–mutualism continuum in nature management and conservation.</jats:p></jats:list-item>
